	 * @example
	 *
	 * ```ts
	 * // Group and count people by their last names
	 * await db.select({
	 *    lastName: people.lastName,
	 *    count: sql<number>`cast(count(*) as int)`
	 * })
	 *   .from(people)
	 *   .groupBy(people.lastName);
	 * ```
